      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is browning, peel and finely slice your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate)your <strong>ginger</strong></p><p>Roughly chop your <strong>tomato[es]</strong></p>",
