    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is golden, transfer it to a clean plate (this will finish cooking in the risotto later) and reserve the pan</p><p>Return the reserved pan to a medium heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> sliced shallot </strong>and<strong> chopped ginger</strong> to the pan with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until softened</p><p>Once softened, add the <strong>chopped tomato</strong> and cook for a further 2-3 min or until the tomato has broken down</p>",
