      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>creamed coconut</strong> (if required!)</p><p>Dissolve your<strong> chicken stock mix</strong> and <strong>chopped creamed coconut</strong> in 700ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[950ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[1.2 L]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> with the <strong>red Thai curry paste</strong> – this is your <strong>red Thai stock</strong></p><p>Trim, then chop your <strong>green beans</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
