    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the tomato has broken down, add your <strong>arborio rice</strong> with <strong>half </strong>your<strong> chilli flakes</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and cook for 1 min, stirring to coat the grains in the mixture</p><p>Add 2/3 of the<strong> red Thai stock</strong> a ladle at a time, stirring continuously for an initial 20 min or until the rice is almost cooked</p>",
