      "instruction": "<p>Cut the <strong>remaining lime</strong> into wedges</p><p>Serve the <strong>red Thai-style chicken breast & green bean risotto</strong> in bowls</p><p>Garnish with a<strong> lime wedge </strong>and sprinkle over the <strong>remaining chilli flakes</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
